channel.title: sabrinakaray - survivor of childhood sexual abuse
channel.description: This podcast is dedicated to all survivors of the trauma of childhood sexual abuse. Episodes will tell the story of denial, self-hatred, guilt, insecurity, and strength associated with the realization and acceptance of being molested and raped as a child.
